<Layouts.app flash={@flash}>
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 mt-5 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <.custom_nav active="chelekom-docs-toast" />
    <div class="lg:col-span-10">
      <.custom_info
        title="Toast"
        description="Customizable toast notifications in Phoenix LiveView provide seamless, non-intrusive user feedback with flexible options for size, color, and positioning."
        mix="mix mishka.ui.gen.component toast"
        github="https://github.com/mishka-group/mishka_chelekom/blob/master/priv/components/toast.eex"
        tags={["Component", "Stateless", "JS-module", "JS"]}
      />
      <.custom_tab id="chelekom-toast-tab">
        <:documentation_panel>
          <.heading2 class="mb-5" id="overview">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#overview"}>
              Overview of the Phoenix and LiveView Toast Component
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The
            <strong>
              Mishka Chelekom toast
            </strong>
            component is a <strong>Phoenix LiveView</strong>
            component that enables developers to create dynamic and customizable <strong>toast notifications</strong>, perfect for displaying brief, non-intrusive messages to users. It offers flexibility in positioning, color, size, and dismiss behavior, making it easy to integrate into any application.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper elements_class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <.button
              size="small"
              phx-click="toast_position"
              phx-value-pos="toast-example-140"
              class="hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
              content_class="flex items-center gap-2"
              icon="hero-sparkles"
              icon_class="size-4"
            >
              Show Collaboration Invite
            </.button>

            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-140"}
              id="success_toast_140"
              rounded="medium"
              horizontal="right"
              vertical="top"
              padding="medium"
              width="max-w-[400px] w-full"
              dismiss_icon_class="size-5"
              class="shadow-lg animate-in slide-in-from-right"
            >
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-[17px] font-medium">LiveView Component</h2>

                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                  Phoenix LiveView team has invited you to collaborate on a new UI component. Would you like to contribute?
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2 mt-5">
                <.button
                  variant="bg-black border border-black text-white hover:bg-black/80"
                  size="py-1.5 px-6 text-[15px]"
                  rounded="small"
                >
                  Join Project
                </.button>
                <.button
                  variant="bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-500/80 border border-rose-600 text-white"
                  size="py-1.5 px-6 text-[15px]"
                  rounded="small"
                >
                  Maybe Later
                </.button>
              </div>
            </.toast>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.cp margin="mt-5">
            This
            <strong>
              <.link
                title="Phoenix LiveView component"
                class="transition-colors hover:text-[#448D96]"
                navigate={~p"/chelekom"}
              >
                Phoenix LiveView component
              </.link>
            </strong>
            also supports various styles, custom triggers, and timers, making it ideal for providing feedback, alerts, or information to users without interrupting their workflow. With its responsive design and ease of use, this toast component enhances the overall user experience and engagement.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_block position="left" color="success" class="my-8" border="medium">
            <.cp>
              By using the class prop, you can apply custom classes or Tailwind CSS classes to customize the components design.
            </.cp>
            <strong>Note:</strong>
            <.custom_inline_code>id</.custom_inline_code>
            is required for each toast.
          </.custom_block>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="base-toast">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#base-toast"}>
              Base Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" code={@code_26}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="natural"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-139"
              >
                Show Base
              </.button>
            </div>

            <.toast :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-139"} id="toast_white_doc_139">
              Toast Base color and variant
            </.toast>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="default-variant-toast">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#default-variant-toast"}>
              Default Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The default style of the
            <.link navigate={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast"}>Mishka Chelekom toast</.link>
            applies customizable colors, making it ideal for providing contextual information to users. With just a single setting, you can select from a range of color options, ensuring easy integration with your application's design.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" code={@code_1}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                color="silver"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-1"
              >
                Show White
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="natural"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-2"
              >
                Show Dark
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="info"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-3"
              >
                Show Info
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="success"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-4"
              >
                Show Success
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="warning"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-5"
              >
                Show Warning
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="danger"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-6"
              >
                Show Danger
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="silver"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-7"
              >
                Show silver
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="misc"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-8"
              >
                Show Misc
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="dawn"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-9"
              >
                Show Dawn
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="primary"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-10"
              >
                Show Primary
              </.button>
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="secondary"
                size="small"
                phx-click="toast_position"
                phx-value-pos="toast-example-11"
              >
                Show Secondary
              </.button>
            </div>

            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-1"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_white_doc_1"
              color="natural"
            >
              Toast Default variant White 1
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-2"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_dark_doc_2"
              color="dark"
            >
              Toast Default variant Dark 2
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-3"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_info_doc_3"
              color="info"
            >
              Toast Default variant Info 3
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-4"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_success_doc_4"
              color="success"
            >
              Toast Default variant Success 4
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-5"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_warning_doc_5"
              color="warning"
            >
              Toast Default variant Warning 5
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-6"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_danger_doc_6"
              color="danger"
            >
              Toast Default variant Danger 6
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-7"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_silver_doc_7"
              color="silver"
            >
              Toast Default variant silver 7
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-8"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_misc_doc_8"
              color="misc"
            >
              Toast Default variant Misc 8
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-9"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_dawn_doc_9"
              color="dawn"
            >
              Toast Default variant Dawn 9
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-10"}
              variant="default"
              id="toast_primary_doc_10"
              color="primary"
            >
              Toast Default variant Primary 10
            </.toast>
            <.toast
              :if={@toast_pos == "toast-example-11"}
              id="toast_secondary_doc_11"
              color="secondary"
              variant="default"
            >
              Toast Default variant Secondary 11
            </.toast>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="outline-variant-toast">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#outline-variant-toast"}>
              Outline Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The outline style of the Mishka Chelekom toast features a border. Using a single setting, you can choose from various color variants to suit your design needs.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" code={@code_2}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
