          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="shadow-variant-toast">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#shadow-variant-toast"}>
              Shadow Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The shadow variant of the Mishka Chelekom toast is similar to the default variant, but it also includes a subtle shadow along with a border and white background in silver mode.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" code={@code_3}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                variant="outline"
