          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="bordered-variant-toast">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/toast/#bordered-variant-toast"}>
              bordered Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The Bordered variant of the Mishka Chelekom card has lighter background and a border. Bordered variant have also white and dark colors which are the same colors in the dark and light mode.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" code={@code_4}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                variant="outline"
                color="silver"
