          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The space prop in the Phoenix LiveView toast component provides various spacing options, including <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>medium</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>large</.custom_inline_code>, and <.custom_inline_code>extra_large</.custom_inline_code>. These options define the vertical spacing between items in the toast, with increasing amounts of space from extra_small to extra_large. If no specific value is provided, the default is set to <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, but custom values can also be applied as needed.
          </.cp>

